<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
<title>RELIGIO PRO — Profil Agen</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/shared/tokens.css">
<style>
  body { background: var(--ink-1000); min-height: 100vh; }
  .wrap { max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 32px 40px 80px; }

  .topbar {
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
    padding-bottom: 18px; margin-bottom: 28px;
    border-bottom: var(--hairline-soft);
    font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--ink-200); letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  }
  .topbar .who { color: var(--gold-300); }
  .topbar a, .topbar button {
    background: transparent; border: var(--hairline-soft);
    color: var(--ink-100); cursor: pointer; text-decoration: none;
    padding: 6px 14px; border-radius: var(--r-sm);
    font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em; text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .topbar a:hover, .topbar button:hover { color: var(--gold-300); border-color: var(--gold-300); }

  .head { margin-bottom: 28px; }
  .head h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 32px; font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--cream-100); margin: 0; letter-spacing: -0.015em;
  }
  .head h1 em { font-style: italic; color: var(--gold-300); }
  .head .sub {
    font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--ink-200); letter-spacing: 0.08em; margin-top: 8px;
  }

  .flash-ok {
    background: rgba(74,143,109,0.10);
    border: 1px solid var(--emerald); color: var(--emerald);
    border-radius: var(--r-sm); padding: 11px 14px; margin-bottom: 20px;
    font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 11.5px;
  }

  .panel {
    background: var(--ink-900); border: var(--hairline);
    border-radius: var(--r-md); padding: 22px 24px; margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .panel h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 18px;
    color: var(--cream-100); margin: 0 0 4px; font-weight: 500;
  }
  .panel .sub {
    font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--ink-200); margin-bottom: 18px; line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .toggle-row {
    display: flex; gap: 14px; align-items: flex-start;
    padding: 12px 0; border-bottom: var(--hairline-soft);
  }
  .toggle-row:last-child { border-bottom: 0; }
  .toggle-row label { cursor: pointer; flex: 1; }
  .toggle-row label .name {
    font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--cream-100); font-weight: 500; display: block;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .toggle-row label .desc {
    font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 10.5px;
    color: var(--ink-200); line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .toggle-row input[type="checkbox"] {
    width: 18px; height: 18px; margin-top: 2px;
    accent-color: var(--gold-300);
  }
  .save-row {
    margin-top: 16px;
    display: flex; justify-content: flex-end;
  }
  .save-row button {
    background: var(--gold-300); color: var(--ink-1000); border: 0;
    padding: 10px 22px; border-radius: var(--r-sm);
    font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase; cursor: pointer; font-weight: 600;
  }
  .save-row button:hover { background: var(--gold-200); }

  .identity {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 120px 1fr; gap: 8px 16px;
    font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 11px;
  }
  .identity .l { color: var(--ink-200); letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; }
  .identity .v { color: var(--cream-100); }
</style>
</head>
<body data-screen-label="03 Agen · Profil">
<div class="wrap">

  <div class="topbar">
    <div>AGEN · <span class="who"><%= user.email %></span></div>
    <div style="display:flex;gap:8px;">
      <a href="/agen">← Dashboard</a>
      <a href="/agen/notifications">Notifikasi</a>
      <form method="POST" action="/logout" style="display:inline;margin:0;">
        <input type="hidden" name="_csrf" value="<%= csrfToken %>">
        <button type="submit">Keluar</button>
      </form>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="head">
    <h1>Profil <em>agen</em></h1>
    <div class="sub">Identitas + preferensi notifikasi.</div>
  </div>

  <% if (flash.ok === 'prefs_saved') { %>
    <div class="flash-ok">✓ Preferensi tersimpan.</div>
  <% } %>

  <div class="panel">
    <h3>Identitas</h3>
    <div class="sub">Profil dasar Anda di sistem. Untuk perubahan (slug, display name, WA, bio), hubungi admin Religio Pro.</div>
    <div class="identity">
      <div class="l">Display name</div><div class="v"><%= profile.displayName %></div>
      <div class="l">Slug</div><div class="v"><code>/p/&lt;paket-slug&gt;?a=<%= profile.slug %></code></div>
      <div class="l">Email</div><div class="v"><%= user.email %></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="panel">
    <h3>Preferensi notifikasi</h3>
    <div class="sub">
      Atur email/notifikasi mana yang Anda terima dari Religio Pro. Catatan: notifikasi tetap masuk ke inbox <a href="/agen/notifications" style="color:var(--gold-300);">/agen/notifications</a> meski Anda matikan email — Anda bisa cek manual kapan saja.
    </div>
    <form method="POST" action="/agen/profile/prefs">
      <input type="hidden" name="_csrf" value="<%= csrfToken %>">
      <div class="toggle-row">
        <input type="checkbox" id="p-stmt" name="notifKomisiStatement" value="true"
          <%= profile.notifKomisiStatement ? 'checked' : '' %>>
        <label for="p-stmt">
          <span class="name">Email laporan komisi bulanan</span>
          <span class="desc">
            Setiap awal bulan, Religio Pro generate laporan komisi periode sebelumnya.
            Email berisi link download PDF. Matikan jika Anda lebih suka cek manual via dashboard.
          </span>
        </label>
      </div>
      <div class="save-row">
        <button type="submit">Simpan</button>
      </div>
    </form>
  </div>

</div>
</body>
</html>
